        <description><![CDATA[# AMAPP - Adaptive Music Application

Automates adaptive music organization for game projects.

**Requirements:** SWS/S&M, ReaImGui, js_ReaScriptAPI

**Features:**
- Render cluster management for batch audio processing
- Wwise and WAXML integration
- Timeline overlay for visual cluster management
- Implementation design workflow]]></description>
